{{Transcript list|Sarah|Sourhog (A Porcine of Interest)|Spria}}

==Starting out==
===Searching the notice board===
* {{tbox|You search through the notice board...}}
* '''Player:''' 'Damaged roof tiles for sale'... 'Come on down to Bob's Axes'... 'Contributions welcomed to Ned's New-Window Fund'...
* '''Player:''' Wait a minute, what's this?
* {{tbox|pic=Scribbled note detail.png|'Keen fighter sought to deal with troublesome monster. Reward offered. Speak to Sarah at the South Falador Farm for details.'}}
* '''Player:''' This could be worth looking into.
* {{tselect|Start the A Porcine of Interest quest?}}
* {{topt|Yes.}}
** '''Player:''' Right, let's go and see what Sarah has in mind.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|No.}}
** {{tact|end}}

====Searching the notice board again====
* {{tbox|You search through the notice board but find nothing more of interest.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Sarah===
====Initial conversation====
* '''Sarah:''' Hello. How can I help you?
* {{topt|Talk about the bounty.}}
** '''Player:''' I've come about the bounty.
** '''Sarah:''' Oh thank Saradomin! It's about time someone responded, something needs to be done!
** '''Player:''' Can you explain what happened?
** '''Sarah:''' Of course. I was making my monthly delivery to The Sheared Ram in Lumbridge, heading east near the Draynor Village crossroads.
** '''Sarah:''' Suddenly, out of the trees came a hulking monster! It chased me for a short distance, but luckily Rosie managed to spook it enough to give me a headstart.
** '''Player:''' Sounds like it must have given you quite the scare!
** '''Sarah:''' It certainly did. I even lost my cart full of farm produce!
** {{topt|What did the monster look like?}}
*** '''Player:''' What did this monster look like?
*** '''Sarah:''' I didn't get a very good look at it I'm afraid. It was getting dark and as soon as I saw it charging at me, I ran.
*** '''Sarah:''' I can still hear the sound, though. A horrible grunting... squealing...
*** '''Sarah:''' Is there anything else you wanted?
*** {{tact|other}}
** {{topt|Any tips on finding this thing?}}
*** '''Player:''' Any tips on finding this thing?
*** '''Sarah:''' Tips...? You're supposed to be the professional monster slayer!
*** '''Sarah:''' Although, I suppose a good place to start would be checking the area I was attacked. See if you can find the remains of my cart.
*** '''Player:''' Ok, yes that could work.
*** '''Sarah:''' Is there anything else you wanted?
*** {{tact|other}}
** {{topt|Whereabouts were you attacked again?}}
*** '''Player:''' Whereabouts were you attacked again?
*** '''Sarah:''' I remember being somewhere near the crossroads, north of Draynor Village.
*** '''Sarah:''' Sorry that I'm not much help. It happened so fast, the whole thing is a bit of a blur.
*** '''Player:''' That's okay. Crossroads north of Draynor... At least I have somewhere to start.
*** '''Sarah:''' Is there anything else you wanted?
*** {{tact|other}}
** {{topt|You mentioned Rosie. Who's that?}}
*** '''Player:''' You mentioned that Rosie spooked the monster. Who's that?
*** '''Sarah:''' Oh, that'll be our lady over there by the fire. She's such a good dog, always accompanies me on deliveries.
*** '''Sarah:''' You can pet her if you like. She's very friendly.
*** '''Sarah:''' Is there anything else you wanted?
*** {{tact|other}}
** {{topt|I think that'll be all for now.}}
*** '''Player:''' I think that'll be all for now.
*** '''Sarah:''' Excellent! Best of luck to you, I'll be waiting right here with your reward.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|quest=No|Talk about something else.}}

====Subsequent conversation====
* '''Sarah:''' Hello. How can I help you?
* {{topt|Talk about the bounty.}}
** {{topt|What did the monster look like?}}
*** {{tact|above}}
** {{topt|Any tips on finding this thing?}}
*** {{tact|above}}
** {{topt|Whereabouts were you attacked again?}}
*** {{tact|above}}
** {{topt|You mentioned Rosie. Who's that?}}
*** {{tact|above}}
** {{topt|I think that'll be all for now.}}
*** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|quest=No|Talk about something else.}}

==Investigating the crossroads==
===Damaged cart===
* {{tbox|It seems as though the monster was trying to run off with some of Sarah's produce. From the looks of things, it was heading north-east.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Cabbages===
* {{tbox|The cabbage is damaged and has begun to yellow.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Carrots===
* {{tbox|The carrot has been slightly gnawed on.}}
* '''Player:''' Weird... What sort of monster charges at someone and then steals a bunch of carrots?
* {{tact|end}}

===Potatoes===
* {{tbox|These potatoes seem to have been largely untouched.}}
* '''Player:''' Would you look at that... Apparently our monster is picky.
* {{tact|end}}

===Broken dead tree===
* '''Player:''' Something pretty big must have come running through here to knock this over.
* {{tact|end}}

===Strange hole===
* {{tcond|If the player does not have a rope in their inventory:}}
** '''Player:''' This looks like the place. It's a long way down, though... I'll need to tie something onto the edge.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has a rope in their inventory:}}
** {{tbox|You tie the rope tightly around a protruding rock.}}
** {{tact|end}}

==Inside the cave==
===Investigating pile of rope===
* '''Player:''' Huh... there's a rope already down here. I hope noone{{sic}} else has got to this monster first.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Sarah after finding the cave===
* '''Sarah:''' Hello. How can I help you?
* {{topt|Talk about the bounty.}}
** '''Sarah:''' Oh it's you, my monster slayer! How goes the quest?
** '''Player:''' I'm still working on it... I've managed to find its lair though.
** '''Sarah:''' Sounds like you're making progress. Take care!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|quest=No|Talk about something else.}}

===Investigating the skeleton===
* {{tbox|The skeleton seems fresh. It looks like the bones have been gnawed clean fairly recently.}}
* '''Player:''' There's also a scrawled note. It's barely readable...
* {{cquote2|This is what I get for exploring uncharted caves. Looks like I'm trapped down here - My entry rope slipped off and now there's nowhere to go but deeper. I think I'd be safer just waiting and praying for rescue. If anyone finds this, get out while you can.}}
* '''Player:''' Well, that's not exactly reassuring.
* {{qact|A level 37 Pig Thing appears behind the player.}}
* '''Player:''' Uhh... Nice piggy?
* {{qact|The Pig Thing sprays acid at the player.}}
* {{tcond|If the player is not wearing Gnome goggles:}}
** '''Player:''' {{overhead|Argh! My eyes!}}
* {{tcond|If the player is wearing Gnome goggles:}}
** '''Player:''' {{overhead|Argh! My eyes! The goggles do nothing!}}
* {{qact|The screen fades to black.}}
* {{tbox|Some time passes...}}
* '''Pig Thing:''' {{overhead|*Sniff* *Sniff*}}
* '''Pig Thing:''' {{overhead|*Snort*}}
* {{qact|The Pig Thing walks away.}}
* '''Player:''' ...
* {{qact|Spria enters the cave.}}
* '''Spria:''' Well then, what do we have here?
* {{qact|Spria approaches the player's unconscious body.}}
* '''Spria:''' Still breathing, eh...?
* '''Spria:''' Seems I came at just the right time.
* '''Spria:''' We'd better get you out of here before that thing returns.
* {{qact|The player wakes up in Spria's house in Draynor Village}}
* '''Player:''' W-what happened? Where am I?
* {{tact|end}}

===Attempting to enter the Sourhog cave after being attacked by the Sourhog===
* '''Player:''' I think I find{{sic}} out more about that monster from Spria in Draynor Village before heading back down there.
* {{tact|end}}

==The Sourhog==
===Talking to Spria===
====Initial conversation====
* '''Spria:''' Oh, you're awake!
* '''Player:''' Who are you? How did I end up here?
* '''Spria:''' My name's Spria and I'm a slayer master. You've had a nasty encounter with a Sourhog.
* '''Player:''' A Sourhog? You mean the giant pig monster?
* '''Spria:''' Precisely. You're extremely lucky that I found you. Another few hours and you'd have been hog chow.
* '''Spria:''' Were you responding to Sarah's bounty too?
* '''Player:''' Yes... It sounded like an easy few coins...
* '''Spria:''' I thought as much. I found you on the floor of the cave, you must have been knocked unconscious.
* '''Player:''' That thing caught me completely off-guard. Normally I can handle myself in a fight, but its spitting attack is pretty fearsome!
* {{tcond|If the player's inventory is full:}}
** '''Spria:''' I have an item for you that will help you on your quest, but you don't seem to have enough space. Come and see me again when you've cleared some room.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player's inventory is not full:}}
** '''Spria:''' The beast's saliva is extremely acidic and your eyes are most vulnerable. It'll cause terrible injuries and leave you unable to attack or defend yourself very well.
** '''Player:''' So how am I supposed to handle that?
** '''Spria:''' Luckily, the Slayer skill provides us with an array of useful equipment and techniques for dealing with... special foes.
** '''Spria:''' In the case of our Sourhog, you'll be needing these.
** {{tbox|pic=Reinforced goggles detail.png|Spria hands you a pair of Reinforced Goggles.}}
** {{tact|receives=[[Reinforced goggles]]}}
** '''Spria:''' This eyewear will protect you from the spitting attack, allowing you to fight the monster on equal terms.
** '''Spria:''' Most enemies have a weakness, too. The Sourhog's thick hide provides excellent protection against slashing and insulates it from magic damage.
** '''Spria:''' You'd be best trying to pierce it with arrows or a stabbing weapon.
** '''Spria:''' Go now, the bounty is all yours to claim. I suggest you recoup your strength and head back to fight it using your new goggles.
** '''Spria:''' If you make it out alive, collect your bounty and then come see me so that we can speak further.
** {{topt|Why are you helping me?}}
*** '''Player:''' Why are you helping me?
*** '''Spria:''' Well, I suppose I could have left you in there to be eaten...
*** '''Spria:''' But you know what that'd make me? A monster. And as a slayer master, that's really not a great look.
*** '''Spria:''' Besides, my father always taught me that knowledge is worth more than gold. I'm happy to sacrifice a few coins in order to pass my experience on to you.
*** '''Player:''' Well, I sure am glad you were there to lend a hand. Thank you!
*** '''Spria:''' Don't mention it. Was there something else?
*** {{tact|other}}
** {{topt|How did I end up back in Draynor Village?}}
*** '''Player:''' How did I end up back in Draynor Village?
*** '''Spria:''' I carried you out and dragged you back here to my house to recover, it really wasn't easy. You're welcome to rest here for as long as you need.
*** '''Spria:''' Was there something else?
*** {{tact|other}}
** {{topt|You said you were a slayer master. What's that?}}
*** '''Player:''' You said you were a slayer master. What's that?
*** '''Spria:''' There are many of us. We're experts in the ancient art of monster slaying. People from across Gielinor come to us for tasks and advice.
*** '''Spria:''' Well... actually, I'm fairly new to this. I've been learning from my father, Turael, for many years. We decided it was finally time for me to continue the family profession.
*** '''Spria:''' Was there something else?
*** {{tact|other}}
** {{topt|Can I have another pair of Reinforced Goggles?}}
*** '''Player:''' Can I have another pair of Reinforced Goggles?
*** {{tcond|If the player has a pair equipped:}}
**** '''Spria:''' No, you're still wearing the last pair I gave you!
**** '''Spria:''' Was there something else?
**** {{tact|other}}
*** {{tcond|If the player has a pair in their inventory:}}
**** '''Spria:''' You've still got the last one I gave you, it's there in your inventory! Those things aren't cheap, you know.
**** '''Spria:''' Was there something else?
**** {{tact|other}}
*** {{tcond|If the player has a pair in their bank:}}
**** '''Spria:''' I know many people all across Gielinor, and my sources tell me you still have the last one in your bank.
**** '''Spria:''' Was there something else?
**** {{tact|other}}
*** {{tcond|If a player does not have a pair in their inventory or bank:}}
**** '''Spria:''' Sure, I have another going spare. Please try to take better care of these.
**** {{tact|"Spria hands you another pair of Reinforced Goggles."}}
**** '''Spria:''' Was there something else?
**** {{tact|other}}
** {{topt|What can you tell me about the Sourhog?}}
*** '''Player:''' What can you tell me about the Sourhog?
*** '''Spria:''' Well, I'm not much of a history buff... But I'll tell you what I know.
*** '''Spria:''' Many years back, before even I was around, there were two rival family farms not far from where we're standing.
*** '''Spria:''' Every year the village would hold a 'Finest Swine in Show' prize at the annual faire.
*** '''Spria:''' The same farmer would win year after year without fail. Driven mad with jealousy, his rival decided to hire a dodgy dark wizard to give him an edge over the competition.
*** '''Spria:''' The wizard attempted to alter the pig's appearance. I'm sure you can guess how well that went!
*** '''Spria:''' Long story short, the mutant, what we now know as a Sourhog, went on a brief rampage and escaped.
*** '''Spria:''' It must have somehow managed to reproduce, because people have reported seeing them in groups.
*** '''Spria:''' Up until now, so long as they were left alone, they'd keep to themselves. Rumors are, they live in deep underground caverns, scavenging what they can find.
*** '''Spria:''' But if they're living so close-by and attacking people on roads, then... they must be getting bold and trying to resurface.
*** '''Spria:''' Was there something else?
*** {{tact|other}}
** {{topt|cond=If the player has gone through any of the above choices:|That'll be all for now.}}
*** '''Player:''' That'll be all for now.
*** '''Spria:''' Very well. Good luck, slayer.
*** {{tact|end}}

====After acquiring the Reinforced goggles====
* '''Spria:''' How goes it?
* {{topt|Why are you helping me?}}
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|How did I end up back in Draynor Village?}}
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|You said you were a slayer master. What's that?}}
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|Can I have another pair of Reinforced Goggles?}}
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|What can you tell me about the Sourhog?}}
** {{tact|above}}

===Attempting to enter the hole without reinforced goggles equipped===
* '''Player:''' I don't want to go back down there without wearing the right equipment!
* {{tact|end}}

===Climbing the blockage===
* '''Player:''' I don't think Spria will be rescuing me this time. If I go in there, I'm fighting this thing to the death!
* {{tselect|Climb over the blockage?}}
* {{topt|Yes}}
** {{qact|The player climbs over the blockage.}}
* {{topt|No}}
** {{tact|end}}

===Attempting to climb the rope after killing the Sourhog but before severing its foot===
* '''Player:''' Before I leave, I should go and collect a foot from that dead Sourhog as proof of my kill.
* {{tact|end}}

===Taking the Sourhog's foot===
* {{tcond|If the player doesn't have a knife or slash weapon:}}
** {{tbox|You try to pull a foot off with your bare hands, but to no avail.}}
** '''Player:''' Perhaps I should go and get something sharp.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player uses something other than a knife or slash weapon:}}
** '''Player:''' I don't think that's sharp enough to cut a foot off...
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has a knife or slash weapon:}}
** {{tbox|pic=Sourhog foot detail.png|You slice a foot off and place it inside your backpack.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has a Sourhog foot in their inventory:}}
** '''Player:''' I've already collected a foot from this thing. I should take it to Sarah.
** {{tact|end}}

===Attempting to re-enter the Sourhog Cave with a Sourhog foot in the player's inventory===
* '''Player:''' I don't need to go back down there right now. I should take the foot to Sarah and collect my reward.
* {{tact|end}}

==Collecting the bounty==
===Talking to Spria===
* '''Spria:''' 'Ello, and what are you after then?
* '''Player:''' I did it! I killed the Sourhog!
* '''Spria:''' Nicely done. Did you collect your reward from Sarah?
* '''Player:''' No, not yet.
* '''Spria:''' Go and collect your reward and then come and speak with me.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Sarah===
* '''Sarah:''' Hello. How can I help you?
* {{topt|Talk about the bounty.}}
** '''Player:''' That monster certainly won't be troubling you from now on.
** '''Sarah:''' Oh that's fantastic news! I'm so relie-
** '''Sarah:''' Wait, how do I know you're not just saying that to get the bounty?
** {{tcond|If the player doesn't have the sourhog foot:}}
*** '''Player:''' I guess I'll go and get you some proof.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|If the player has the sourhog foot:}}
*** '''Player:''' How about this as proof?
*** {{tbox|pic=Sourhog foot detail.png|You pull the foot out of your backpack and show it to Sarah.}}
*** '''Sarah:''' Eugh! Yes, that certainly looks about right!
*** '''Player:''' Indeed, the smell is... something quite special.
*** '''Sarah:''' I'll probably just give it to the dog.
*** '''Sarah:''' I'm glad you made it back. Some strange woman in a hood came asking about the job shortly after you left. I didn't really want her back in here.
*** '''Sarah:''' Anyway, thank you so much! Here's your reward.
*** {{tbox|pic=Coins 250 detail.png|Sarah hands you a heavy pouch of 5,000 coins.}}
*** '''Player:''' Perhaps I should speak with Spria and tell her that the monster's been dealt with.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|quest=No|Talk about something else.}}

==Finishing up==
===Talking to Sarah before telling Spria about the bounty completion===
* '''Sarah:''' Hello. How can I help you?
* {{topt|Talk about the bounty.}}
** '''Player:''' Feeling better now that the monster's gone?
** '''Sarah:''' Very much so! Thanks again. What was it, anyway?
** '''Player:''' It was a Sourhog. A giant bipedal pig creature!
** '''Sarah:''' Oh crumbs... I think I've heard of those... My grandfather was always rambling on about them.
** '''Sarah:''' Nevermind... that's all history now. Weren't you heading off to see Spria?
** '''Player:''' Yes, I suppose I should get going.
** '''Sarah:''' Safe travels!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|quest=No|Talk about something else.}}

===Talking to Spria===
* '''Spria:''' 'Ello, and what are you after then?
* '''Player:''' I did it! I killed the Sourhog and collected the bounty from Sarah.
* '''Spria:''' Very impressive, slayer. I'm glad that the goggles served you well.
* '''Spria:''' Although, these Sourhogs often live in primitive tribes. I fear that where there's one, there's likely to be more to follow.
* '''Spria:''' We may have to monitor that lair from time to time to keep their population in check.
* {{tact|continue}}
* {{tcond|If the player has unlocked the ability to craft the [[slayer helmet]]:}}
** '''Spria:''' I've noticed that you've unlocked the ability to craft slayer helms. From now on, when assembling one, fasten a pair of Reinforced Goggles to the eye holes to gain their benefit.
** '''Spria:''' While we're on the topic, I can upgrade any of your existing slayer helms now.
** {{qact|The screen briefly fades to black}}
** '''Spria:''' That should do the trick.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{qact|Congratulations! Quest complete!}}
* {{tcond|If the player does not have a slayer task:}}
** '''Spria:''' By the way, you seem to have a natural talent for killing monsters. Would you like a new slayer task now?
** {{tselect|Do you want a slayer task from Spria?}}
** {{topt|Yes}}
*** {{tact|Player receives a Slayer task.}}
** {{topt|No}}
*** '''Spria:''' Very well, come back if you change your mind.
* {{tcond|If the player has a slayer task:}}
** {{tmissing}}

